OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781111161
OL,3,COvercrowded prisons in Wales
OL,4,Cundermining safety, MPs warn
OL,6,FOvercrowding and staffing challenges
OL,7,Fhave undermined staff and prisoner
OL,8,Fsafety in Wales, a new report warns.
OL,10,FA report by the Welsh Affairs
OL,11,FCommittee highlighted "serious
OL,12,Fconcerns" about the Welsh prison
OL,13,Festate.
OL,15,FRuth Jones MP, chair of the committee,
OL,16,Fsaid the "system that too often fails
OL,17,Fthe people it is meant to serve" and
OL,18,Fthat "it's a system struggling with
OL,19,Fpopulation pressures, staffing
OL,20,Fshortages, and increasingly complex
OL,21,Fdemand."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
