OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781111161
OL,3,COvercrowded prisons in Wales
OL,4,Cundermining safety, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe report said improving staff
OL,7,Fretention is necessary to alleviate
OL,8,Fpressures, while increasing time spent
OL,9,Fout of cells is also vital to ensure
OL,10,Fsuccessful rehabilitation for
OL,11,Fprisoners.
OL,13,FThe committee warns that addressing
OL,14,Fthese challenges is made more complex
OL,15,Fby the division of responsibilities
OL,16,Fbetween the UK and Welsh Governments
OL,17,Fand is calling for close cooperation
OL,18,Fbetween the two to support offenders
OL,19,Fin turning their lives around.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781111161
OL,3,COvercrowded prisons in Wales
OL,4,Cundermining safety, MPs warn
OL,6,FIt recommends that the Ministry of
OL,7,FJustice (MoJ) meet with Welsh justice
OL,8,Funions to identify the main barriers
OL,9,Fto recruiting and retaining staff, and
OL,10,Fsays that concerns regarding pay and
OL,11,Fconditions should be addressed as soon
OL,12,Fas possible.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government said it
OL,15,F"intend(s) to engage with the UK
OL,16,FGovernment on these issues in a
OL,17,Fconstructive manner."
OL,26,@wD@HpmwD@Jpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
