PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781111161
OL,3,COvercrowded prisons in Wales
OL,4,Cundermining safety, MPs warn
OL,6,FIt has also called for the justice
OL,7,Fsystem to be "fully devolved to
OL,8,FWales", saying: "Only through
OL,9,Fdevolution can we provide services in
OL,10,Fa joinedup and efficient way that
OL,11,Fdelivers for the people of Wales."
OL,13,FHowever, the Ministry of Justice said:
OL,14,F"The current devolution settlement
OL,15,Fensures the people of Wales benefit
OL,16,Ffrom the shared resources of a larger
OL,17,Fjustice system, and funding for
OL,18,Fcertain youth justice initiatives is
OL,19,Fbeing devolved.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781111161
OL,3,COvercrowded prisons in Wales
OL,4,Cundermining safety, MPs warn
OL,6,F"Our focus is on continuing to fix the
OL,7,Fjustice system, including improved
OL,8,Fcoordination of rehabilitation support
OL,9,Fto cut reoffending and meet the needs
OL,10,Fof Welsh communities."
OL,12,FMPs also called for a review to
OL,13,Finvestigate why the imprisonment rate
OL,14,Fin Wales has consistently been shown
OL,15,Fto be higher than that seen in
OL,16,FEngland, as well as in most of Western
OL,17,FEurope.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
